          {
            "_key": "ad8cc47e-24b9-4fda-b535-e3296ab0edaa",
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "責任感と倫理観：人の命に関わる仕事を通じて、高い責任感と倫理観が培われます。"
          }
        ],
        "level": 1,
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "bullet"
      },
      {
        "_key": "k5l6g1h2i3j4",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "f8c89422-acfe-4842-97ba-04b1fa9f9e56",
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "体力と精神力：タフな医療現場で働くことで、心身ともに強くなります。"
          }
        ],
        "level": 1,
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "bullet"
